One of the nation’s foremost chemical and specialty fluids and production solutions group, Eunisell, has joined the big league after being certified ISO 9001:2015 by Bureau Veritas. Mr Chika Ikenga, the Group Managing Director, expressed delight with the certification and emphasised that the company’s world-class standards will increase. “Customer satisfaction has always been the foundation of Eunisell’s brand promise. Now it is mandated and we look forward to continuing to help our customers’ businesses grow through service excellence,” he said. Halogen security receives ISO 9001:2015 certification, promises more innovation ISO reaffirms confidence in BoI’s processes LADOL Becomes First Company In West Africa To Get ISO 45001, 9001, 14001 Certification